interface       -   ViewPager.PageTransformer
single method   -   transformPage (View page, float position)
parameter       -   position

setPageTransformer  -   to set PageTransformer on viewPager
--------------------------------

transformPage() -   called at each screen's transition, once for each visible page ( i.e. 3 )

position    -   indicates where a given page is located relative to the center of the screen
            -   dynamic property that changes as the user scrolls through the pages
            -   [,-1)       -   page is way off-screen to the left
            -   [-1 , 1]    -   visible
            -   (1,]        -   page is way off-screen to the right


https://developer.android.com/training/animation/screen-slide.html#depth-page
---------------------------------------

setAlpha(alpha);
setTranslationX(translationX);
setScaleX(scale);
setScaleY(scale);
